<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[الضِّفِنّ]</span>: الأحمق العظيم الخَلْق، الكثير اللحم.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> إِن الضِّفِنَّ القصير،<span class="c5"> ويقال:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>الأول أصح.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فِعِلَّةُ]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[ن]</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c4">[الضِّفِنَّة]</span>: امرأة ضِفِنَّة: أي ضخمةٌ كثيرة اللحم.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
